{"tid":1361461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"注意！光復元朗，政府勢成最大贏家","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:41:46.000Z","uid":18258,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fe068dbe1d6fd2898fe9fe5aba6133c66b314657","tid":1361461,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"光復元朗其實市民係無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算市民唔係自行用任可手段光復，只要迫到警察出手做野然後食花生結果都係光復左元朗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當天遊行打正旗號係要反鄉黑光復元朗<br />\n如果遊行入人村搞事，話要搞人祠堂，鄉黑一定全力對抗<br />\n到時候警察介入，警察到時會點做？<br />\n<br />\n1.警察同以往一樣，搵防暴搞示威者<br />\n但在場又有鄉黑，如果有示威者（市民）走左入村俾鄉黑打，其他市民因警察鎮壓而支援唔到落單入村嘅示威者，政府將會成為協助鄉黑打市民嘅幫兇<br />\n到時候戰術失誤又證明政府無力管治<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>政府輸</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.1 如果警察見到以上情況，又唔想俾人話係鄉黑幫兇，咁就要殺入村打鄉黑救市民。咁到時候佢救完示威者（市民）應該要拉定要放呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（我諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n到時候就變左鄉黑警大戰，市民就可以行埋一邊食花生，成功光復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果就係市民出嚟自發救元朗迫政府做野，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>市民贏政府輸</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果警察打贏，警察拉哂啲鄉黑成功光復，市民將成最大贏家<br />\n政府就會得罪鄉黑，市民又只會覺得你應份而唔會轉軚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府都係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且之前有人話如果同時間香港有幾個地方一齊亂的話係無足夠警力控制局面<br />\n到時候如果鄉黑發動報復全港到處搞事，全港大亂變無政府狀態<br />\n政府輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者鄉黑求自保被迫將警黑勾結嘅內幕爆出嚟攬炒<br />\n政府又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，萬一警察打唔贏敗退，咁又證明政府無力控制場面，否定唔到黑社會治港嘅事實<br />\n都係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.2如果市民係和理非表達光復訴求，但警察都係出手鎮暴搞市民<br />\n市民無搞祠堂，只係幫元朗爭取清除黑勢力都俾黑警搞<br />\n市民出師有名又俾人打，又一次俾全世界睇到佢濫暴<br />\n又輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時候或者有大批市民避警察入村避難<br />\n村民提供保護<br />\n市民村民connected<br />\n共同對付黑警濫暴，又同黑勢力割蓆（或者短暫共同抗暴而同黑勢力）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復成功政府輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（未必會發生不過都係一個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.今次唔攪示威者，同市民合作對付鄉黑<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢個唔太可能發生，就算係市民可以行埋一邊食花生，成功光復<br />\n或者市民到時會同時搞9警察，令警察打輸俾鄉黑<br />\n又或者村民市民connected<br />\n結果都係一樣<br />\n警察打贏打輸都係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復行動成功政府輸<br />\n<br />\n3.警察放軟手腳，專登等市民鄉黑互相廝殺<br />\n到時候市民自力光復<br />\n俾人睇到黑社會治港<br />\n政府無力控制<br />\n<br />\n市民輸政府輸<br />\n<br />\n4.警察分散力量打哂鄉黑同市民<br />\n如果到時警察同時開兩條戰線，示威者只要放軟手腳同佢慢慢玩<br />\n唔駛勇武都夠搞到佢地死下死下<br />\n結果係點都好只要我地能夠be water全身而退<br />\n市民都係贏<br />\n狗輸政府輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.警察好似616或者721咁唔出現<br />\n即係直接認輸，到時遊行其實係咁2完左就散又好有衝突發生又好<br />\n政府都係好肉酸<br />\n無存在價值/無政府仲好過有<br />\n<br />\n呢個遊行只要搞得成，基本上政府已經係點做都輸<br />\n啲克警只要忍唔住做錯少少野搞亂個遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做唔到野俾市民罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果政府唔想輸，佢而家要做嘅係嚇到星期六無人敢去元朗，只要當日搞唔成，形勢就唔會有改變。所以出盡力放風叫人唔好去<br />\n例如：<br />\n10間大學出聯署聲明 叫我地唔好去元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1360753/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1360753/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n或者到時候放軟手腳，等市民成功拆人祠堂，到時候鄉黑就會同市民群眾鬥群眾，政府可以等收割，等你全部人打完再將黑社會同勇武派一網打盡。（唔好俾佢咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n727一定要出去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者討論下政府可以點贏，大家傾下點避免<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469fbe1c1daa33f0e3de533f260f03ae078603c1","tid":1361461,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44e1c35fc07a854a5b0cb82983c2c4ad3ecbc6c5","tid":1361461,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a26a7b6b464836b0583fae1ef58f3379ac407f","tid":1361461,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:05.000Z","msg":"推一推<br />\n希望有人一齊討論下"},{"pid":"cdd370f435dc7eee4c1a224c580399110f7fece3","tid":1361461,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:21:48.000Z","msg":"如果官黑有合作，就要迫到佢裡外不是人<br />\npopo成為磨心<br />\n壓力大到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67246861e0022990e630e8e988de7b3dfcaaef43","tid":1361461,"uid":209449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"諗唔到理由唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec42c0e26895f396240c4e00b59352cc034de98","tid":1361461,"uid":188899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"聚焦反警黑勾結"},{"pid":"123c7826558aac2bfca510b7b0608375922a3091","tid":1361461,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果到時可以拉攏村民支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15aa00d064c14c8dc557d60bb0e67ae0d42da613","tid":1361461,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:49:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"edee2c9fadb5f1af875e6c39b9a5affa7a507d02","tid":1361461,"uid":231905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"唔好主動入村啦"},{"pid":"c0dddc4c87d8677c479be0845545193baed4223f","tid":1361461,"uid":18258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eec42c0e26895f396240c4e00b59352cc034de98","tid":1361461,"uid":188899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"聚焦反警黑勾結"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:59:48.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得唔需要講反黑警勾結<br />\n<br />\n黑警勾結本身就係錯，唔駛刻意再講反對<br />\n應該係抗議黑警勾結因爲唔應該發生既事竟然被揭發"},{"pid":"49b4caea183cf251f4f6c4337623dc3be04d2a04","tid":1361461,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:01:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d95cb0771fb94645295f9b1daedca7e71848a1a","tid":1361461,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"好game theory feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8e49285e4d76b94862e6fcf3cb90326335d5f4","tid":1361461,"uid":212182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"而家真正將警隊逼到死角，揸正做又會得罪鄉黑，唔揸正又再令警隊威嚴變負數。所以727去元朗勢在必得！！"},{"pid":"7b36270951c69fe86a966cbadd657fbfb2ea3f39","tid":1361461,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edee2c9fadb5f1af875e6c39b9a5affa7a507d02","tid":1361461,"uid":231905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"唔好主動入村啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime